---
title: Falafel and Chicken Tenders Couscous with Roasted Tomatoes, Olives and Feta
description: This Middle Eastern-inspired couscous is a cause for celebration! Packed with oven-roasted falafel, blistered tomatoes, briny olives, feta and garlic-tossed cucumber, this dish has checked off every flavour box!
